front.title: •BoShek (V)
front.gametext: Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. BoShek's deploy cost may not be increased. During battle, may use 1 Force to subtract 1 from opponent's just drawn destiny or cancel an attempt to cancel and redraw a destiny. Immune to attrition < 3.
front.lore: Rogue pilot. Outlaw starship tech. Has secret lab in Mos Eisley. He bragged about beating Han Solo's Kessel Run record. Left fringe life behind after meeting Obi-Wan Kenobi.
